
'''Xolile Tshabalala''' (yavutse ku ya 9 Mata 1977) ni umukinnyi wa [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] yepfo<ref>https://briefly.co.za/35945-xolile-tshabalala-biography-age-baby-husband-actress-generations-pictures-instagram.html</ref>.  Azwiho uruhare muri serivise nyinshi za tereviziyo zizwi cyane zirimo ''4Play:Sex Tips for Girls'', ''Secrets & Scandals'', ''Blood & Water'' and ''Housekeepers''.<ref>https://www.thecityceleb.com/biography/celebrity/actress/the-biography-of-xolile-tshabalalay/</ref><ref>https://mlasa.com/actors/xolile-tshabalala/</ref>  

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavukiye i Vrede, muri Leta y'Ubuntu.  Yiswe  na nyirakuru ubyara se. Yarangije mu Ishuri Rikuru ry’Ubuhanzi  afite icyubahiro ndetse na 'Best Performer Performer<ref>https://thenation.co.za/bio/xolile-tshabalala-biography/</ref>'. 

== Umwuga ==
Mu masomo ye mu ishuri ry’igihugu, Xolile yagize amahirwe yo gukina na Thembi Mtshali-Jones, ari naho yamubereye umujyanama<ref>https://www.kaya959.co.za/xolile-tshabalala-politicians-are-using-us-to-shoot-targets-for-their-own-gains/</ref>. Bakinnye hamwe mu ikinamico ''Crucible'' yerekanwe ku Isoko ry'Isoko . Uyu mukinnyi wa filime nawe yakinnye<ref>https://www.news24.com/drum/celebs/news/actress-xolile-tshabalala-on-her-latest-role-and-life-in-lockdown-20200724</ref>. Yakinnye kandi mubikorwa byinshi bya Televiziyo nka, na Soul City season 7, aho yakinnye mushiki we Zama. Ntabwo bigarukira gusa kuri ecran , Xolile yakinnye kandi mumikino itandukanye irimo "Undi Mwana".<ref>https://www.sowetanlive.co.za/entertainment/2021-09-17-xolile-tshabalala-is-fit-for-purpose-thanks-to-granddad/</ref><ref>http://africultures.com/personnes/?no=51385</ref>  

Mu 2005, yafashe ikiruhuko cyo gukina. Nyuma yagiye muri [[Amerika]] kwitabira ishuri rya Filime rya New York .<ref>https://mlasa.com/actors/xolile-tshabalala/</ref> Yagarutse muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo mu mwaka wa 2010 akina 'Noma' muri televiziyo ya ''4Play: Sex Tips for Girls.'' Hanyuma yakinnye cyane yerekana 'Mandi Mbalula' muri serial ''Fallen'', ikinamico yo mu 2011. Muri 2013, Xolile yagaragaye nka 'Gugu' muri ''High Rollers'' yacaga kuri SABC 3<ref>http://www.philmphelablog.com/2017/02/xolile-tshabalala-makes-tv-comeback.html</ref>.<ref>https://thenation.co.za/bio/xolile-tshabalala-biography/</ref><ref>https://mlasa.com/actors/xolile-tshabalala/</ref>  

